```plantuml
@startuml zalando-incubator_fabric-gateway

actor User
participant "FabricGateway CRD" as CRD
participant "IngressDerivationChain" as IDC
participant "StackSetOperations" as SSO
participant "GatewayWebhookRoutes" as GWR
participant "Kubernetes API" as KAPI
participant "IAM Service" as IAM

User -> CRD: Define API configuration
CRD -> IDC: Derive Ingress resources
IDC -> SSO: Discover services via StackSets
SSO -> IDC: Return service info
IDC -> KAPI: Create/Update Ingress
IDC -> GWR: Request webhook validation
GWR -> KAPI: Perform validation
KAPI -> GWR: Validation result
GWR -> IDC: Validation success/failure
IDC -> IAM: Request authentication
IAM -> IDC: Authentication result
IDC -> User: Return gateway status

@enduml
```